    "In this appendix section, k is measured from the Dirac point of the relevant layer and valley for convenience.",
    "The action of a symmetry operator will be written in the matrix form asÔd † k Ô-1 = d † Ôk U Ô(140)for some unitary or anti-unitary operator Ô. Matrix multiplication is implied on the right hand side.",
